answer:
Builds widgets based on the latest snapshot of interaction with a Future:

   ```dart
   FutureBuilder<String>(
     future: fetchData(),
     builder: (context, snapshot) {
       if (snapshot.hasData) {
         return Text(snapshot.data!);
       }
       return CircularProgressIndicator();
     },
   )
   ```

